{"tid":138746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國婦女商店地上撿20英鎊被判盜竊罪","createTime":"2017-02-28T23:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T02:41:06.000Z","uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84cafd72a4960afc1aa87cc4b9d119ef167bc160","tid":138746,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T23:31:50.000Z","msg":"一名在一個商店裏撿到一張20英鎊鈔票的婦女被判偷盜罪。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的尼可&middot;貝利（Nicole Bailey）在特倫特河畔斯托克的布勒頓的一站店（One Stop）一個分店中撿到了鈔票，而這張鈔票是由一名顧客從現金提取機上取款後掉落的。<br />\n<br />\n貝利女士在北斯塔福德郡的司法中心審判中看到閉路電視的證據後認罪。<br />\n<br />\n據報道為她辯護的律師團隊說，應該以警察警告的形式處理這個案件。<br />\n<br />\n住在布勒頓的貝利女士現在必須支付20英鎊的賠償，額外20英鎊的受害者附加費用，以及135英鎊的法庭費用。<br />\n<br />\n這次偷盜發生在去年8月8日。<br />\n<br />\n斯塔福德郡警察的高級督察凱倫&middot;史蒂芬森敦促任何撿到丟失現金的人都應該&quot;正確行事&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;從道德上說，正確的做法是交還丟失財產，這樣當事人能夠有充分機會找回丟失財產。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;這是某人辛苦掙來的錢，我們要努力支持社區中所有的受害者。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-39122818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-39122818&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=2dfe4c17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-39122818&h=de263f67\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-39122818</a>"},{"pid":"65d5af8e252a247e44af939556a65f12c1bdcd4a","tid":138746,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/news/woman-nicole-bailey-kept-20-note-one-stop-burton-stoke-on-trent-criminal-record-staff-poketed-a7603576.html?cmpid=facebook-post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Fwoman-nicole-bailey-kept-20-note-one-stop-burton-stoke-on-trent-criminal-record-staff-poketed-a7603576.html%3Fcmpid%3Dfacebook-post&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=8168ff8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.independen